com.interpss.dc.pv.module

Interface PVModule

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AbstractPVModule, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IPVModule, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PVModuleImpl

    public interface PVModule
extends AbstractPVModule
    A representation of the model object 'PV Model'. PVModule input date is stored in the PVModuleItems list. Before calculation, the initData() is called to consolidate the input date into the PVModel object, always as a set of IV curve data points.

    The following features are supported:

    • Iv Curve Type
    • Equiv Pv Model
    • Pv Items
    See Also:
    PVModulePackage.getPVModule()
